        <abstract>
            <p>Wishes CD would enlarge on the doctrines of [Pyotr Simon] Pallas about the various races of dogs having come from several distinct wild species or sub-species.</p>
            <p>Suggests organisms have a latent principle of improvement which is brought out by selection or breeding.</p>
        </abstract>
